{"id":256563,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/中国时刻-司马南：被扔鞋的知识分子/","date":"2012-10-12T04:29:58Z","modified":"2012-10-12T04:29:58Z","title":"中国时刻 | 司马南：被扔鞋的知识分子","content":"<p>2012年的10月7号，司马南在海南大学发表演讲。演讲一开始司马南就说：若有人有不同意见，要扔鸡蛋鞋子，都理解并拟予以尊重。不料一语成谶，即将结束的自由提问环节，观众席中有青年因不满言论权利不平等怒而向其扔鞋。而事件发生后，立即在网上引起了轩然大波。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><object width=\"480\" height=\"370\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"pluginspage\" value=\"http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://you.video.sina.com.cn/api/sinawebApi/outplayrefer.php/vid=87572839_2091945350_O0rnRyIxWTLK+l1lHz2stqkP7KQNt6nniWO1slahJgtZQ0/XM5GRZdgA4iHVCdkEqDhATJ86cvwu1BQ/s.swf\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><embed width=\"480\" height=\"370\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"http://you.video.sina.com.cn/api/sinawebApi/outplayrefer.php/vid=87572839_2091945350_O0rnRyIxWTLK+l1lHz2stqkP7KQNt6nniWO1slahJgtZQ0/XM5GRZdgA4iHVCdkEqDhATJ86cvwu1BQ/s.swf\" pluginspage=\"http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" /></object></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">视频<a href=\"http://video.sina.com.cn/v/b/87572839-2091945350.html\" target=\"_blank\">地址</a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,13770],"tags":[16022]}